OL,5, Education unions have accused the      
OL,6, government of risking a "full-blown    
OL,7, funding crisis" for schools with their 
OL,8, latest offer on teachers' pay.         
OL,10,FThe Department for Education has       
OL,11,Fannounced a rise of 5% for teachers and
OL,12,Fmore for early-career salaries.        
OL,14,FFive unions representing the majority  
OL,15,Fof teachers said the plans would put   
OL,16,Fpressure on stretched school budgets   
OL,17,Fand exacerbate staffing shortages.     
OL,19,FThe government has described the offer 
OL,20,Fas the most generous for years.        
